# VEHICLE::IS_BIG_VEHICLE

## Summary
Checks if the vehicle big e.g plane

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns true if MF_IS_BIG (strModelFlags 0x8) handling model flag is set.
